{"tid":2003781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鬧市持大聲公罵特首 12歲男童被捕","createTime":"2020-05-06T04:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T13:25:30.000Z","uid":127067,"like":5,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5745496bcdd7c67738edf14d38f260f754482aac","tid":2003781,"uid":127067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:44:22.000Z","msg":"有網民本日1日號召在旺角等5區發起「天馬行動」進行快閃堵路等，當日未見有示威者堵路，但旺角卻有一名男童手持「大聲公」坐在電單車司機後，與司機一起用粗口罵行政長官林鄭月娥及警隊，司機則手拿一疊500元紙幣。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查後，昨日以公眾地方行為不檢罪拘捕一名涉案12歲男童，據悉該名男童曾因盜竊等被捕。警方現仍追尋司機下落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1763769/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%AC%A7%E5%B8%82%E6%8C%81%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%B2%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B5%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96-12%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1763769%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E9%25AC%25A7%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25B2%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25BD%25B5%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596-12%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KREYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=567de9d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1763769%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E9%25AC%25A7%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25B2%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25BD%25B5%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596-12%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595&h=c3f3cb60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1763769/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%AC%A7%E5%B8%82%E6%8C%81%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%B2%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B5%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96-12%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95</a>"},{"pid":"ca846b456c7c8e49bc1dd0c7db7b02f9b96aa28d","tid":2003781,"uid":224561,"like":14,"dislike